            <title>[LU-9713] e2fsprog on SUSE need to require libcom_err, libss</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9713</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;installing e2fsprog from lustre did not pulling the same version of libcom_err, libss. this results in failure like this&lt;/p&gt;

